title: Fall/Winter 2015 O'Neill MUTANT
description: Accept no limitations. O’Neill’s unique Modular Closure system makes the Mutant and D’Lux Mod the most versatile wetsuits in our line. The Mutant and D-Lux Mod are constructed of UltraFlex DS and UltraFlex Firewall in the front and back. Making the Mutant warmer and more flexible than ever before. Two suits in one, now go get some.
